place.name: ATHELSTANEFORD
place.gazetteerText: Athelstaneford, par. and vil., in co. and 3½ miles N. of Haddington, 5077 ac., pop. 762; P.O. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
